l the registered hooks, in order, on the emitted alarm.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-reset_alarms\"><a href=\"#val-reset_alarms\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> reset_alarms : <span>unit <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Reset the alarm logs, this should be used only for post analysis</p></div></div>"}